<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">To add, remove, or reorder a field you just add/remove/move an object in <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">FORM_FIELDS</code>. To create a completely different form — say a vehicle registration — you change the title and swap the field list. The engine below rebuilds everything automatically.</p>
