<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>You need a local web server.</strong> The easiest options:</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Option A — VS Code (if you have it)</strong>
