:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Both files are ready to download fresh.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">The truncation likely happened because you copied and pasted the HTML content into GitHub's editor instead of uploading the file directly. To avoid it this time:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
