ansparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Here's how to structure it — a simple table in Word that I can read reliably and convert to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">form.json</code>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Create a table with these 4 columns:</strong></p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Field Label</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Type</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Pattern</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Required</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Full name</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">alpha-full</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Date of birth</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">split</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">NN-MMM-NNNN</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Address</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">address</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">City &amp; province</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">city-province</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Social Insurance Number</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">split</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">NNN NNN NNN</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Postal code</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">split</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">ANA NAN</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">RAMQ number</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">split</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">AAAA NNNNNNNN</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Yes</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Rules for each column:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Field Label</strong> — whatever you want shown above the field, any text</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Type</strong> — must be exactly one of: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">alpha-full</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">free-full</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">split</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">address</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">city-province</code>, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">dropdown</code></li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Pattern</strong> — only needed for <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">split</code> fields, leave blank for all others</li>
<li class="whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Required</strong> — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Yes</code> or <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">No</code></li>
